<h2 id="what-is-med-spa-tech-stack">🏥 What Is a Med Spa Tech Stack?</h2>

A med spa tech stack is the collection of software tools that power your entire operation—from the moment a prospect books a consultation to the final payment and follow-up. Unlike general spa software, med spa tools must handle clinical documentation, before/after photo management, consent forms, controlled substance tracking, and medical-grade compliance requirements.

The core components include:

- **Practice Management/EMR:** Clinical charting, treatment notes, photo documentation
- **Online Booking:** Client-facing scheduling with service-specific intake
- **Point of Sale & Billing:** Payment processing, memberships, packages
- **Inventory Management:** Injectable tracking, product management
- **Marketing Automation:** Email/SMS campaigns, lead nurturing
- **Reputation Management:** Review generation, response management
- **Reporting & Analytics:** Multi-location dashboards, provider performance

The challenge most operators face: medical features live in one system, spa features in another, and marketing in a third. This creates data silos that kill personalization and waste staff time on manual reconciliation.

