Pabau's built-in marketing covers basics—appointment reminders, birthday messages, simple drip campaigns. For sophisticated lead nurturing, treatment-specific re-engagement, and multi-touch attribution, consider layering in a dedicated platform.

Look for tools that integrate with Pabau's API to pull treatment history and personalize messaging based on past services. A client who received lip filler 11 months ago should get different messaging than someone who's only had facials.

<h3>Reputation Management</h3>

Automated review requests are built into Pabau, but dedicated reputation tools offer review monitoring across platforms, AI-powered response suggestions, and competitive benchmarking. For practices in competitive markets, this visibility matters.

